name: #00018 portrait of Daddy 211015
description: #00018 portrait of Daddy 211015 was created on 15th October 2021 This drawing was a picture of Daddy in pen, Iris has also produced some writing patterns around the drawing but when asked what she wrote, she "don't know" sadly, The enigma that is a toddler! This is NFT number 18 released by the Youngest Artist in the NFT World, Iris. Age at release - 3 years old.
